                    <value>&lt;br /&gt;
Hi&amp;nbsp;{{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Your follow-up bloodwork is now due.&amp;nbsp;Please find attached a follow-up lab order form.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You can print it out and take it to your nearest Quest Diagnostics along with your insurance card for service.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.questdiagnostics.com/&quot;&gt;CLICK HERE&lt;/a&gt; to find your nearest Quest Diagnostics.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color:#000000; font-size:16px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; text-align:start; white-space:normal; background-color:#ffffff; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;This form is not valid at LabCorp locations.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
To ensure accurate results, please fast for at least 8 &amp;ndash; 10 hours prior to your blood draw.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:start&quot;&gt;
&lt;ol start=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#ffffff&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:yellow&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif&quot;&gt;Schedule blood draw 4-5 days post testosterone injection&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;If using HGH, inject it within a 2-5 hour window of blood draw&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;Please take&amp;nbsp;ALL&amp;nbsp;10X Health prescribed oral medications in morning prior to your blood draw&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif&quot;&gt;If using any cremes, do not apply to arms the morning of your blood draw.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;font style=&quot;color:#000000; font-family:arial; font-size:16px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; text-align:start; white-space:normal; background-color:#ffffff; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial,Sans-Serif&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color:#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Important - 10X Health is not responsible for any lab tests that your health insurance carrier may not cover.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:start&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-ligatures:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:#ffffff&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration-thickness:initial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration-style:initial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration-color:initial&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif&quot;&gt;After your blood test, you can retrieve your results from Quest Diagnostics&amp;#39; website.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
